<C>__{ben }
<D>__{gary?}
<A>__{ben comes a bit closer. his gaze freezes when he realizes that gary is not standing in front of the mirror with his face pressed against it, but he is behind the mirror, inside! ben steps back, terrified. he doesn't know how to interpret this new phenomenon. ben gathers his courage and returns in front of the mirror knock, knock, knock... he hits the mirror with his fist, as if it were merely a glass window behind which gary lewis was standing, on the other side no reaction. ben strikes the mirror harder. knock, knock, knock... the former night watchman turns around slowly towards ben, revealing his face little by little...}
